If you can make through my rambling… here’s a little explanation of what’s poppin. Shout out ALL the homies who have came through and helped over the last month. Still a lot to do. It’s the ultimate DIY with MASSIVE support from @dgk. Keep an 👀 on DGK YouTube channel for edits dropping on a fairly consistent basis. Love ya’ll 💯💯💯👊🏽

Had to make sure this was the first thing you see when you open the door, and before we skate. 🙏🏼 Legends Never Die ❤️ big shout out to @ozay_moore for painting this amazing mural. It means the world to me. #keenanmilton #keithhufnagel #pepemartinez #haroldhunter
Getting closer to that @dgk YT VLOG DROP. Make sure you keep your 👀 peeled. First ever DIY all granite indoor spot. 💯💯💯💯💯
Can’t wait to get the LOVE granite ledges done. In the meantime, starting to get used to these hips.

Episode One “The Build” is now live on @dgk YT. Direct link in my bio. Big thank you to DGK for the support on this. Also @poole.customcarpentry without your ramp building knowledge and experience/expertise, my shit would have fell apart already. Shout out @romieswd, @m1keh0ag for the hours and hours of help laying down cutting/fitting all the granite. My back and knees are still sore. What a nightmare. Haha. Shout out @mikeson__ for killin the edit and bringing together all the homies. A lot of us worked mad long days/nights to get this together. Shout out @brian_panebianco for the exclusive Philly delivery. But yeah… this vlog type stuff is new to me, it will be a pretty consistent as far as video drops go. Please dont hesitate to give me feedback. I’m a need it moving forward!! 💯💯💯💯💯
